Titolo: Persona 5 Strikers

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Persona 5 Strikers is an action role-playing game developed by Omega Force and P-Studio and published by Sega. The game is a crossover between Koei Tecmo's Dynasty Warriors franchise and Atlus' 2016 role-playing game Persona 5 and is set half a year after the events of the original Persona 5. It follows Joker and the rest of the Phantom Thieves of Hearts as they investigate a series of mysterious events involving people across Japan.
Persona 5 Strikers was released in Japan for Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4 in February 2020, with a worldwide release for those consoles and Microsoft Windows in February 2021. The game received generally favorable reviews from critics and sold over 1.5 million copies by June 2021.

